Accountant
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/06 10:27:14
Ref. JB3046992
Job Description
The candidate must possess:
• A college diploma / degree in Finance / Commerce or Hospitality management.
• In-depth knowledge of operational characteristics, services and activities of accounting in the hospitality industry;
• Thorough understanding of complex principles and practices of hotel accounting for preparing financial reports on Uniform system of Accounting.
• Good knowledge of principles and standard practices of complex financial record keeping and reporting
• Good knowledge of principles of budget preparation and control.
• Must be able to interpret and apply pertinent local laws, codes and regulations.
• Must have two years’ work experience in a hospitality establishment.
